{"tid":1698712,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【拍到皺晒眉】李嘉欣演楊貴妃多波折 髮型太大問題多","createTime":"2019-11-07T16:34:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T11:16:26.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c1e64b37b6e29f2a7cd6801d5fdff4b45abb6068","tid":1698712,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-07T16:34:10.000Z","msg":"49歲的大美人李嘉欣，08年嫁予許晉亨後專心做少奶奶，鮮有再參與幕前演出，早前，《延禧攻略》製作人于正公開了李嘉欣的楊貴妃造型劇照，宣佈嘉欣參與其製作的綜藝節目《演技派》，而嘉欣的楊貴妃造型亦令大家眼前一亮，更被譽為「最靚的楊貴妃」。<br />\n<br />\n李嘉欣復出，相信大家亦好期待，而《演》方面最近亦推出了嘉欣扮演楊貴妃的預告片，只見一身貴妃打扮的嘉欣，與飾演唐玄宗的吳鎮宇正在拍攝，不過由於戲服太繁複，令坐下來的嘉欣顯得極不自在，不過在旁的鎮宇亦非常有風度，跟在場的工作人員解釋說：「穿古裝就是這樣了。」<br />\n<br />\n當嘉欣終於坐好後，鎮宇又問工作人員，她最後需不需要將頭挨在自己的膊頭上？然後鎮宇就拍一拍膊頭，叫嘉欣試一下位置看看舒不舒服，不過由於嘉欣有一個比頭還要大的髮型，她試位後就說：「很難舒服。」之後鎮宇就出手摸了一下嘉欣的腮骨位，叫她轉用這位置來挨在膊頭上，不過今次嘉欣的頭飾又頂到鎮宇的頭，而最後嘉欣再嘗試伏下，將身體挨在鎮宇的大腿上營造恩愛的畫面，不過今次就因為頭太大而擋住鎮宇的臉而被叫停，令到她也忍不住笑。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20191107/large/1573137385_56e8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20191107%2Flarge%2F1573137385_56e8.jpg&h=99fb990d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191107/60242665\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191107%2F60242665&d=Z9XWEpuBYzNDjlwSEAyqKy3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=c1797616\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20191107%2F60242665&h=308b3c28\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191107/60242665</a>"},{"pid":"4b0f2202c3709a8433aff4e05bb8ae2ac7853107","tid":1698712,"uid":182930,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T01:35:53.000Z","msg":"收得錢叫你做就做啦，咁多嘰gut<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d503c84a2288f542fe120937ed99c88223c53ae","tid":1698712,"uid":76063,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T01:39:57.000Z","msg":"西"},{"pid":"79a5556ffc707a2615223a802f4a762096828dca","tid":1698712,"uid":158411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T01:40:54.000Z","msg":"我"},{"pid":"85ed627aae3c4fd83946f327cbb01dd749fd1ef4","tid":1698712,"uid":247494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T01:41:51.000Z","msg":"太老，不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15938ba3d9b12a43c89bd632e01e68db216a6019","tid":1698712,"uid":203057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79a5556ffc707a2615223a802f4a762096828dca","tid":1698712,"uid":158411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T01:40:54.000Z","msg":"我"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T01:42:39.000Z","msg":"真"},{"pid":"7ba6447465ecc8eb77a1c6d9adc97321733306f1","tid":1698712,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d503c84a2288f542fe120937ed99c88223c53ae","tid":1698712,"uid":76063,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T01:39:57.000Z","msg":"西"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T08:13:07.000Z","msg":"女"},{"pid":"cf17720bcebe89d38198478b90742896804c900b","tid":1698712,"uid":85965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"15938ba3d9b12a43c89bd632e01e68db216a6019","tid":1698712,"uid":203057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79a5556ffc707a2615223a802f4a762096828dca","tid":1698712,"uid":158411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T01:40:54.000Z","msg":"我"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T01:42:39.000Z","msg":"真"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-08T08:14:53.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"d4b57dbe20e87fbfd4b24df4da447aa182dfdafa","tid":1698712,"uid":151616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf17720bcebe89d38198478b90742896804c900b","tid":1698712,"uid":85965,"l